<br>
Primal Remedy <br>
Magician level 44 <br>
<br>
Mana: 200<br>
Amount healed: 80 per tick, 6 ticks = 480<br>
ratio: 2.4<br>
<br>
<br>
Now the damage healed per second is not very comparable for the rest of this thread, but look at the ratio compared even to the level 52 pet heal.<br>
I've gone to casting this spell at the beginning of a battle, and if it's not a very tough mob my pet is at 90% or better after most battles.  Nice.<br>
